{
  "id": 3478,
  "name": "Consecrated Scorpion",
  "desc": "<p>An arthropod that has mutated after feeding from greater lifeforms.</p><p>Lifeforms are governed by the laws of evolution, Consecrated Beasts exploited these rules by being fortunate enough to discover a long-dead carcass of a greater being before any of their competition ever did. Animals and humans often have far more in common than the latter is willing to acknowledge.</p>",
  "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/19/194600931/ea2958c04ec8f00a5ec2d9f8dc1410e4_2499644417485243979.png",
